**Summary:** This documentation explains how to instrument account-level reporting in Amplitude using various methods including SDKs (Android, iOS, JavaScript), server-side APIs (Identify API with `groups` key, HTTP API with event-level groups), Segment integration with Group Type/Value Traits, and the Group Identify API for creating/updating groups with property operations.

